Advanced NMR Systems Inc said itextended the exercise period for its class A and class Bwarrants by one year.    The company said class A warrants, entitling the purchaseof one share in Advanced Systems and one class B warrant atfour dlrs per unit, will now be execrisable unitl Aug 18 1988.    The class B warrants, entitling the purchase of one shareof common stock at six dlrs per share, are now exercisableunitl Aug 18 1989. Reuter&#3;